{"id": "1409446495115153529", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "딜러용 명륜으로는 상당히 좋을거 같긴합니다.", "timestamp": "2025-08-25T07:57:10.685000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1409446598848548915", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "문제는..... 그렇게 카드를 많이 쓰는 딜러용 명륜을 이미 준비되어있는 상태라면 좀 그렇죠", "timestamp": "2025-08-25T07:57:35.417000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
